         OWASP incorrectly matches the Prometheus CPE against micrometer.
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <suppress until="2026-12-31Z">
        <notes>
            CVE-2026-42154: micrometer-registry-prometheus 1.15.11 — CVE published
            2026 with no patched version available. OWASP matches Prometheus CPE
